data.description: Turn Key RAMBLER in the desirable Berry Farms community! This home is about as adorable as it comes. Fresh updates throughout the home including a BRAND NEW ROOF this month (November 2023), both bathrooms remodeled in 2021, fresh paint & all laminate floors throughout. Home features 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, a large fully fenced backyard, great patio for entertaining & generous grass area in backyard to play your summer lawn games. Two car attached garage, convenient access to I-5, Hwy 9, tons of shopping including the outlet malls, restaurants and so much more! LOW HOA dues round out this amazing and adorable house as your perfect opportunity to stop renting and build your own equity and for you to call this HOME!
